  2,208,"Mo a moagye adie, monfa moakoma nyinaa nwura Islam mu, na monhwŒµ yie na moanni Õªbonsam anamÕªn akyi. NokorŒµ sŒµ ÕªyŒµ motamfo a Õªda adi pefee"
